messages.text: Hi. Sorry to bother you, but I noticed that you've been playing this game a bit. Hopefully that means you like it. Either way, I would really appreciate some feedback to help me make it better. Send an email (jeremy@zengm.com) or join the discussion on Reddit or Discord.
